{"tid":1066961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵撞車原因投票","createTime":"2019-03-18T08:27:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T09:09:44.000Z","uid":42751,"like":8,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3f803ffbebe3f7dfb725bad4962683c090854e31","tid":1066961,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:27:20.000Z","msg":"如果答案係後者嘅話，政府同港鐵都一定唔敢公佈真相<br />\n鬼佬寫嘅軟件有問題：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n華為嘅信號零件出事：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1c13e87751099f68944ed66848d6946931d4e7","tid":1066961,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:29:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1836b7f5b4bc230bd3b92e198da40654b5180d1b","tid":1066961,"uid":17641,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:29:48.000Z","msg":"港獨勢力干擾訊號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f6220df8af8ae19cd0502a81ee052bef0ad229","tid":1066961,"uid":52200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:30:02.000Z","msg":"似係local P仔寫嘅programme出事。"},{"pid":"9412d9e4544a9bf296dfce44d86c6cfe96c5e4cb","tid":1066961,"uid":112416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:30:55.000Z","msg":"港鐵高層都係有反佔中思想"},{"pid":"51f17ac8e19706ab2b4c5af6dc10786e6f27b0de","tid":1066961,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90f6220df8af8ae19cd0502a81ee052bef0ad229","tid":1066961,"uid":52200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:30:02.000Z","msg":"似係local P仔寫嘅programme出事。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:37:03.000Z","msg":"pway?"},{"pid":"e71d4795290b661f2004931132d09d2ed9bf54fa","tid":1066961,"uid":52200,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"90f6220df8af8ae19cd0502a81ee052bef0ad229","tid":1066961,"uid":52200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:30:02.000Z","msg":"似係local P仔寫嘅programme出事。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:37:47.000Z","msg":"新信號系統採用「通訊為本列車控制技術」（Communications Based Train Control，CBTC），<span style=\"color: red;\">以「移動區間」（Moving Block）原理運作</span>，在確保列車之間有安全距離的情況下加密列車班次，提升載客量。新系統利用現代無線通訊技術（Wifi）以列車所發出的信號替代軌道上的固定信號，系統、列車與青衣車務控制中心之間可作無間斷實時雙向溝通，將列車位置及車速等資料傳給中央電腦，透過電腦運算後將信息回傳給列車以維持列車之間的安全距離，<span style=\"color: red;\">不需考慮軌道上的「固定區間」（Fixed Block）；較現有「距離區間」（Distance-To-Go）信號系統更有效率</span>，軌道內的空間得以盡用，避免因前車未完全離開區間而浪費可行空間，從而實現加密班次。新系統亦可減少路軌旁的裝置，從而減少維修。為免WiFi信號受到干擾，承辦商將系統保安設計提高至接近國防級別。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://hkrail.fandom.com/wiki/%E4%BF%A1%E8%99%9F%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrail.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E8%2599%259F%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4M7TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=8704fb8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkrail.fandom.com/wiki/%E4%BF%A1%E8%99%9F%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1</a><br />\n<br />\n就咁睇個system complexity 由P變左做NP。<br />\n路軌當中仲有D cross-over 嘅位。有可能係外判出去嘅vendor (AP /P) 寫control programme 嘅時候冇cater到 cross-over 位置嘅「移動區間」嘅計算，照當係普通linear model (單軌單線行車) 咁計。"},{"pid":"789e2d22541bca5d4684032723adb04981feaa00","tid":1066961,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:53:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5fcc17b2f6b8a341384abb8e243b9c83e4d3a1","tid":1066961,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9412d9e4544a9bf296dfce44d86c6cfe96c5e4cb","tid":1066961,"uid":112416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:30:55.000Z","msg":"港鐵高層都係有反佔中思想"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:55:53.000Z","msg":"反佔中思想嚴重荼毒企業管理者思維同判斷力"},{"pid":"ba9efa644b445fdbc27f9cd2abf5f539d4dd4772","tid":1066961,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e71d4795290b661f2004931132d09d2ed9bf54fa","tid":1066961,"uid":52200,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"90f6220df8af8ae19cd0502a81ee052bef0ad229","tid":1066961,"uid":52200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:30:02.000Z","msg":"似係local P仔寫嘅programme出事。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:37:47.000Z","msg":"新信號系統採用「通訊為本列車控制技術」（Communications Based Train Control，CBTC），<span style=\"color: red;\">以「移動區間」（Moving Block）原理運作</span>，在確保列車之間有安全距離的情況下加密列車班次，提升載客量。新系統利用現代無線通訊技術（Wifi）以列車所發出的信號替代軌道上的固定信號，系統、列車與青衣車務控制中心之間可作無間斷實時雙向溝通，將列車位置及車速等資料傳給中央電腦，透過電腦運算後將信息回傳給列車以維持列車之間的安全距離，<span style=\"color: red;\">不需考慮軌道上的「固定區間」（Fixed Block）；較現有「距離區間」（Distance-To-Go）信號系統更有效率</span>，軌道內的空間得以盡用，避免因前車未完全離開區間而浪費可行空間，從而實現加密班次。新系統亦可減少路軌旁的裝置，從而減少維修。為免WiFi信號受到干擾，承辦商將系統保安設計提高至接近國防級別。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://hkrail.fandom.com/wiki/%E4%BF%A1%E8%99%9F%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrail.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E8%2599%259F%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4M7TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=8704fb8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkrail.fandom.com/wiki/%E4%BF%A1%E8%99%9F%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1</a><br />\n<br />\n就咁睇個system complexity 由P變左做NP。<br />\n路軌當中仲有D cross-over 嘅位。有可能係外判出去嘅vendor (AP /P) 寫control programme 嘅時候冇cater到 cross-over 位置嘅「移動區間」嘅計算，照當係普通linear model (單軌單線行車) 咁計。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T09:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73136f94ac55c7fdb7cc8437a0ead03b63280649","tid":1066961,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T09:09:44.000Z","msg":"both"}]}